      <h2>Custom-Built Solutions for Tourism & Hospitality</h2>
      <p>We develop AI agents, build integrations, and create purpose-built software to solve your unique operational challenges</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <!-- Top Row: 4 Cards -->
      <div class="features-row features-row-top">
        <div class="feature-card animate-on-scroll" onclick="openFeatureModal('email')">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>AI Email & Communication Bots</h3>
          <p>Custom-built AI agents handle emails, chats, and calls 24/7, reducing response time by 90%</p>
